---
title: Shawarma-Inspired Plant-Based Ground Protein Meatballs with Roasted Veggie Couscous and Feta Cheese
description: This deconstructed wrap is inspired by the classic Middle Eastern dish. With savoury plant-based ground protein meatballs, roasted veggies, couscous and salty feta cheese, it's equally as tasty and colourful as the iconic handheld.
